{"tid":1574400,"cid":5,"subCid":11,"title":"神助攻：穆迪報告認為香港經濟倚賴的自治和法治已經受中國政府所影","createTime":"2019-09-16T11:42:31.000Z","updateTime":"2019-09-16T14:25:31.000Z","uid":293289,"like":32,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":20,"replies":[{"pid":"498695475229f6ef7b14bc4a2996eb0b0942e570","tid":1574400,"uid":293289,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-16T11:42:31.000Z","msg":"（突發！重要助攻！好多媒體都忽略了！）評級機構穆迪剛剛宣布，下調評級展望，由「穩定」降至「負面」。<br />\n<br />\n關於今次下調評級展望，狠人睇返份穆迪今次份報告，有一段相當重要：Consistent with this, Moody's has previously noted that a downgrade could be triggered by a shift in the current equilibrium between the SAR's economic proximity to and legal and regulatory distance from China. <span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">The decision to change Hong Kong's outlook to negative signals rising concern that this shift is happening, notwithstanding recent moves by Hong Kong's gove</span></span>rnment to accommodate some of the demonstrators' demands.<br />\n<br />\n意思是，<span style=\"font-size: large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">穆迪認為雖然香港政府最近撤回了修例，但仍然見到香港經濟倚賴的自治和法治已經受中國政府所影響。</span></span>（7月份穆迪報告曾經指出示威活動有助香港制衡中國政府的影響，保持一國兩制的高度自治地位）<br />\n<br />\n不過狠人發現大部分媒體都沒有報導呢個重點！請大家廣傳！！！ <br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://m.moodys.com/research/Moodys-changes-outlook-on-Hong-Kongs-Aa2-rating-to-negative--PR_409149\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fm.moodys.com%2Fresearch%2FMoodys-changes-outlook-on-Hong-Kongs-Aa2-rating-to-negative--PR_409149&d=9iHhAbkmMxvvE1I2I23sbYICM%2BRBTk%2Byah4LEbU4uIE%3D&h=b9ae5dd2\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://m.moodys.com/research/Moodys-changes-outlook-on-Hong-Kongs-Aa2-rating-to-negative--PR_409149</a>"},{"pid":"095232d1d211dd85e219c43f6aef1036da109029","tid":1574400,"uid":33930,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-16T11:42:47.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/pvsTHEi.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FpvsTHEi.jpg&h